About SOAR Conference

Our Mission

SOAR empowers healthcare leaders to develop exceptional leadership capabilities, fostering innovation and excellence in patient care delivery and organizational management.

Our Vision

To cultivate a network of distinguished healthcare professionals who drive transformational change in their organizations and communities through exemplary leadership.

Our Values

Integrity, Innovation, Collaboration, Excellence, and Compassion - the fundamental principles that guide exceptional healthcare leadership.
